    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short-barrelled long guns, held at the shoulder or in the hands, using pistol ammunition and capable of fully automatic fire.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
